{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard If this check box is selected, the customer is considered a one-time customer. When a customer is a one-time customer, you can enter address and tax information, AR customer contact specifications, output media as well as payment method and payment address information at invoice entry and connect this information to the individual invoice. Documents such as reminders, payment advices and interest invoices will be grouped by the address ID. (\b Note\b0 : The language for these documents and the country for selections/groupings are fetched from the master record and not from the individual invoice.)\par
One-Time Customers are only supported if the PAYLED module is installed. They are not supported in the ORDER and PRJREP module.\f0\par
}
